nature of its architecture,

00:02:27.510 --> 00:02:30.740
passive techniques for heating,
cooling, ventilation and day

00:02:30.740 --> 00:02:34.510
lighting, use of renewable
sources of energy,

00:02:34.510 --> 00:02:37.020
efficient and environment
friendly practices

00:02:37.020 --> 00:02:40.210
during construction
and post occupancy,

00:02:40.210 --> 00:02:43.990
use of [INAUDIBLE] materials,
and occupant health, safety,

00:02:43.990 --> 00:02:45.180
and comfort.

00:02:45.180 --> 00:02:47.610
