having higher efficiency

00:14:30.330 --> 00:14:33.440
through the green building
index in Malaysia.

00:14:33.440 --> 00:14:37.630
And GBI can become a guiding
tool for buildings in Malaysia

00:14:37.630 --> 00:14:40.090
to sustain their energy
efficient character

00:14:40.090 --> 00:14:41.990
throughout their lifespan.

00:14:41.990 --> 00:14:45.160
In the next 50 years
our energy demands

00:14:45.160 --> 00:14:47.340
